<plot>A film about the dissolute priest, known by the nickname "Saint Prevezis". Its starting point was the filming of the theatrical performance of Makis Antonopoulos and is further enriched with certain auxiliary material: interviews with the parents whose children took refuge in monasteries, views of the spectators of the theatrical performance, and comments on the journalistic research of Spyros Karatzaferis, on which the film was based.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?403861</url></doc>
